<http://www.spektrix.com/theatreaquarius/event/29201ACCPRBMSLVHDLHKGSRKDGGQQMTJM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "2025 Fall Acting: Take The Stage (grade 9-12)";
  schema:description """
	<h1>TAKE THE STAGE (Grade 9 to 12) NEW FORMAT!</h1><h2>An Actor’s Palette</h2><span><br/></span>Explore the full spectrum of performance in The Actor’s Palette- a ten-week acting program designed for teens ready to deepen their craft and expand their skills across four essential pillars of the actor’s toolkit: Acting for the Camera, Shakespeare, Improv and Character Study. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Taught in a supportive and ensemble-based environment, the class culminates in a studio performance of selected work for family and friends. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Dates: Tuesday, September 9 to Tuesday, November 18<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Times: 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Location: 190 King William Street, Studio Theatre<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>East Studio Entrance<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No classes: Tuesday, October 14<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Cost: $297.00 plus HST<span><br/></span>
""";
