<http://www.spektrix.com/theatreaquarius/event/29002ACNTLSKNGDCHSRHKKLPKRSQSNPMK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Jeans n' Classics: Heartland";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Jeans 'n Classics </h1><span><br/></span><h2>Heartland: Current & Classic Country</h2><span><br/></span>From the raw edge of Miranda Lambert to the timeless soul of Johnny Cash, Heartland is a thrilling journey through the best of country music—then and now. Jeans ’n Classics pairs powerful vocals with symphonic arrangements to celebrate chart-toppers from Carrie Underwood, Keith Urban, Zac Brown Band, Alison Krauss, Dolly Parton, and more. With lush orchestration and unforgettable storytelling, this concert blends the grit of modern country with the heart of its roots—capturing everything from heartbreak ballads to boot-stomping anthems.<span><br/></span>
""";
