<http://www.spektrix.com/theatreaquarius/event/12001ALNGHTPHGCKCMSTDNQBDRDVTJPQB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Time Capsule";
  schema:description """
	<h1>THE TIME CAPSULE   </h1><span><br/></span><h2>A new comedy by Matt Murray  </h2><span><br/></span><h2>Directed by Mary Francis Moore </h2><span><br/></span><h2>October 1 to October 18, 2025</h2><span><br/></span>When a group of five strangers gather in a Church basement in Hamilton to discuss what should go inside a soon-to-be-buried time capsule, what could possibly go wrong?  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The answer….Everything! Throughout one outrageous and hilarious night, relationships old and new are pushed to their limits as this incompatible group tries to agree on… well, anything whatsoever.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h1>Ticket prices include HST and fees</h1>
""";
